{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"dc68d022846048d6b519ff4ded1d8fa8ff8bf6f1c3d6855a2cac309a71e7728a","slug":"thinking-in-sync","location":"/story/think/thinking_in_sync.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"当团队的思考开始高度同频","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/story/think/thinking_in_sync.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/story/think/thinking_in_sync.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"thinking_in_sync.md","url":"/thinking_in_sync-d7ff6e032db3c2f1af47d8c8865d92cd.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是一篇关于思考与认知的品牌故事，记录团队在思考内容和方法上的逐渐同频，以及给我们带来的影响。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"R2visMo6ak"}],"key":"Y1edOAHnYq"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"创始人是公司思考力的源头","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"c5M6cIPF1A"}],"identifier":"id","label":"创始人是公司思考力的源头","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"ThQVxlascT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从 3 月开始启动开源自己和公司的行动。一开始是从自己的视角开始，逐渐进入公司视角，又进入各个领域的本质深入输出，一个认知基础设施逐渐开始成型。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"a2FAFgUrpa"}],"key":"yS3j1uZMD8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"两个月以来，第二大脑的演化完整地复现了公司的思考框架的发展过程。先是我产生各种各样的思考主题和思考方式，成熟以后逐渐形成公司的框架，又形成了超出公司的更本源的框架。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"DJVgsmvaBd"}],"key":"yAE6RhGOcQ"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原始思考流意外启发团队顿悟","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"Q7f5Q9Tynk"}],"identifier":"id","label":"原始思考流意外启发团队顿悟","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"T17OC7aSb9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我逐渐地开始发现，真正有价值的，从来不是产生了什么结果，而是思考的过程具备启发性。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"ScA0Nd8TbC"}],"key":"NiMCJXFofh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"COO 姗总是第一个被启发的人。她有天看了我的思考记录，和我说特别解压，几乎都是她在困扰的问题。这是我第一次发现我无意中的记录竟然产生了这么大的效果，以及我们的思考居然已经这么同频了。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"HVO5h6Sy7p"}],"key":"onSfTJvq7H"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的助理小周是范式的固化者。昨天刚好有许多顿悟和突破，她看完了以后也顿悟了自己的困扰。她最近在帮助我构建整个体系的过程中，反复提出说感觉缺了一些什么，看了我的原始思考流以后找到了把所有碎片串起来的拼图。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"szg2xIDaSG"}],"key":"Qaxq65f7JB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高密度的原始思考蕴含高价值的隐性经验\n这些变化超出预期。我在发明这些实践的时候，初衷只是倾倒高密度的原始想法、减少心理压力。可是没想到居然成为了最关键的启发器。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"KRh8iZoJzl"}],"key":"DgbowuqFKG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"仔细想来，经过十年的积累，我的思考已经成为了高密度的原矿。她们都说，可能我自己没注意的细节，就能成为启发她们的关键。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"TKpSGfQdwe"}],"key":"R1Ef83g82M"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这些“细节”就是我们一直在找的“隐式经验”，一旦当这些经验开始扩散以后，它们也开始以空前快速的方式显形。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"RZwRQ6wakL"}],"key":"BA7nbpvu9R"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这意味着，一旦我们找到一条从创始人到一线的思考流水线工厂，那么我只需要每天记录原始思考流，就可以驱动整个团队不断地突破认知瓶颈。对于一个知识密集型的团队，这将会是不可估量的效率提升。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"ZHvcnPc9rn"}],"key":"yV5caTp9u6"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"强制团队学习秘书处的习惯","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"o5tPJd1Lp0"}],"identifier":"id","label":"强制团队学习秘书处的习惯","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"lGruVjDCSJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"想要把偶发的启发变成团队的习惯并不容易，因为思考是痛苦的。秘书处自发形成，是因为他们面临着巨大的经营压力。但是整个公司尚未形成成型的思考。","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"qKM45rPicA"}],"key":"Pm4PjU04Yo"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"想了很多办法都没用，我决定回归最简单粗暴的方式：通过我在团队的权威，要求公司所有人向秘书处看齐。","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"z4znlucMob"}],"key":"hDDq0f5Cq8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因为我已经甚少直接管理具体事务，因此我的少量干预具备很强的检查和示范作用。这种职能转变也为未来秘书处转型提供了参考。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"ptdf0OQXRt"}],"key":"aNQjRcRqws"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"既然秘书处因为直面经营压力而快速成长，那么就强迫所有人面对就好了。通过这种方式，我们将会获得对于我们的“民主”与“法治”模式下最需要的“公民意识”——全员经营意识。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"ZlmcRchd6P"}],"key":"RiFjoVKaq6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这一小段实际上回答了我们创立公司代表大会制度以来困扰我们几年的终极问题——如何确保这个制度依赖的全员经营意识可以不丢失？","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"Q0czCktGJE"}],"key":"M7ix47sT7t"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"答案也非常简单优雅——用制度强迫每个人遵守规则，用切身利益赏罚建立经营意识的培养，直到它成为不可撼动的系统惯性为止。","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"PD6NaVeUKG"}],"key":"B7CM22aZFN"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"创始人的权威作为推动改革的动力","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"X4IyXcmXLk"}],"identifier":"id","label":"创始人的权威作为推动改革的动力","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"E7jOZUCjeT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"看起来是一个悖论。但是之所以可以有效，很大程度上是因为市场习惯与老板和员工的旧关系，而非公司和成员的新关系。","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"naYcjcE5su"}],"key":"OPIeSWVl8R"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在这种时候，我的权威就要用来推动那些新关系未产生之前作为起点的旧关系。从老板要求过渡到公司惯例，这需要的恰恰是我的示范来“立宪”。","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"caz3TBcnZl"}],"key":"RKQIQcFa8V"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当系统代替我约束团队成员的时候，我自然而然地可以继续退回到我的舒适区，然后继续去寻找下一个突破点。这就是我作为创始人不可替代的职业意义。","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"TG4qtKTEWm"}],"key":"X1SVtcv0mn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我不禁在想，那这个系统没有我该如何进化呢？或许反过来说，当这个系统没有我也可以自我进化的时候，也就是我可以真正卸下责任功成身退的时候。","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"HhGZaBlOvf"}],"key":"XbRMSmTw4p"}],"key":"g1dtpCgCC0"}],"key":"fcGzufdMLS"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}